snippet.title: Super Beat Sports | Net Ball IRL
snippet.description:
Coming to Nintendo Switch October 12!

Hope you’ve been practicing your serve, it’s time for Net Ball in #SuperBeatSports! Keep the volley going with perfect timing, don't let those aliens psych you out! Super Beat Sports is a collection of five sports-themed mini games with a twist - everything is musical. That means that you’ll need swing, volley, and score to the music in order to come out on top.

Learn more at www.superbeatsports.com
